                <note rend="inline" type="source">367.1164 Brusa School Trial/16: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Turkey</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Grew</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Constantinople</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1928-02-14T20:00:00+02:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 14, 1928—8 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received February 14—5:45 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>19. Department’s 13, February 9, 6 p.m. Four pupil witnesses heard today.
                    Hearings postponed until March 5. Goodsell optimistic.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Grew</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
